everywhere","kind":"article","title":"AutoFill everywhere","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10115-AutoFill-everywhere","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Discover how to implement AutoFill in your app and help people enter their information into fields easily, privately, and securely. Learn how to help the system to give better suggestions that tailor to your app’s functionality: offer smart location suggestions within a navigation app, for example, or provide a private way to input contact information into fields from the QuickType bar."}],"role":"sampleCode"}}}